#: ../../administrators.rst:1114
msgid ""
"AIPs cannot be created or deleted through the Storage Service interface, "
"though a deletion request can be submitted through Archivematica that "
"must be approved or rejected by the Storage Service administrator. To "
"learn more about deleting an AIP, see :ref:`Deleting an AIP "
